The use of feedback links also suggests a possible connection to networked systems (cs.NI). The paper proposes achievable schemes and outer-bounds for different interference models, which involves system design and optimization (cs.SY). The use of lattice codes in the Gaussian case suggests a possible connection to multimedia systems (cs.MM).
